13:55.167 --> 13:57.545
That brat was so desperate,
she said whatever she could.

13:58.546 --> 14:02.049
Attention.
All players, please follow the staff

14:02.132 --> 14:04.176
to your designated positions for the game.

14:19.650 --> 14:20.818
Ali.

14:20.901 --> 14:23.988
